{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelSignalName"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelSignalName\/itemsChanged"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelsignalname\/itemschanged"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when a change has occurred to the menu.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"itemsChanged"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The only changes that can occur to a menu is that items are removed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or added.  Items may not change (except by being removed and added","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"back in the same location).  This signal is capable of describing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"both of those changes (at the same time)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal means that starting at the index "},{"code":"position","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"removed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"items were removed and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"added"},{"type":"text","text":" items were added in their place.  If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"removed"},{"type":"text","text":" is zero then only items were added.  If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"added"},{"type":"text","text":" is zero"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then only items were removed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As an example, if the menu contains items a, b, c, d (in that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"order) and the signal (2, 1, 3) occurs then the new composition of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the menu will be a, b, _, _, _, d (with each _ representing some"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"new item).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Signal handlers may query the model (particularly the added items)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and expect to see the results of the modification that is being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reported.  The signal is emitted after the modification.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"title":"DBusMenuModelSignalName.itemsChanged","externalID":"s:3GIO23DBusMenuModelSignalNameO12itemsChangedyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Case","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusMenuModelSignalName/itemsChanged":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelsignalname\/itemschanged","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelSignalName\/itemsChanged","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when a change has occurred to the menu.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"DBusMenuModelSignalName.itemsChanged","role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusMenuModelSignalName":{"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusMenuModelSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelSignalName","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelsignalname","title":"DBusMenuModelSignalName","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusMenuModelSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}